            <div class="odd-title">
                <h2>General Informations</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="general-rule-paragraph">French Coast Stamina 2 is an international online tournament taking place from now on until June 4th 2016.</p>
            <p class="general-rule-paragraph">It is splitted into 2 divisions: High and Hope. Each one has its own ranking.</p>
            <p class="general-rule-paragraph">FailOn, ITG timings and life (exceptions for life can be made on particular public machines). Play when you want, play what you want.</p>
            <p class="general-rule-paragraph">Send scores in the <strong>French Toast Stamina facebook group</strong>, or at <strong>frenchcoaststamina@gmail.com</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
