<div class="container even-container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="high_division col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 evenIndexPage">
            <div class="even-title">
                <h2>High Division</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="high_division_rules_paragraph">The division is consituted of 10 songs made for the tournament. These 10 songs are 10-minutes mixtapes with original and existing charts (see more info on credits page)</p>
            <p class="high_division_rules_paragraph">Each chart has all difficulties stepped, which make for 50 charts.</p>
            <p class="high_division_rules_paragraph">Edit steps are not counted in the ranking and supplement the song:
            Despair EDIT has footspeed in it, Fast Animu Music Expert features Gate Openerz v3, the Edit features the v2, FASTER Animu Music has a harder version to it (maybe a 20).</p>
            <p class="high_division_rules_paragraph">
            For each song the scoring system is:
            <strong>Diff adj * 9.09 * (Score * 100 + (BPM - 100) / 5)</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="bullet-list-even-diff-adj">
                <li class="list-line-diff-adj">Diff adj is calculated this way:</li>
                <li class="list-line-diff-adj">Expert = 1</li>
                <li class="list-line-diff-adj">Hard = 0.8</li>
                <li class="list-line-diff-adj">Medium = 0.65</li>
                <li class="list-line-diff-adj">Easy = 0.5</li>
                <li class="list-line-diff-adj">Beginner = 0.4</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="high_division_rules_paragraph">All tries are worth their scores. Failing does not matter, but FailOff has to be disabled.</p>
            <ul class="bullet-list-score-example">
                <li class="list-line-score-example">Scores examples:</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">94.30% pass on Hallucinogen Expert is worth 948 points.</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">95.19% pass on Neurostreamz Medium is worth 636 points.</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">31.16% fail on Dernier Voyage Expert is worth 501 points.</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">31.16% fail on Dernier Voyage Beginner is worth 201 points.</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example"></li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example"> Only the best score on one song counts:</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">93,08% on Hallucinogen Easy = 469 Points</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">89,92% on Hallucinogen Medium = 590 Points</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">76,32% on Hallucinogen Hard = 628 Points</li>
                <li class="list-line-score-example">Score is 628 points for Hallucinogen.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="high_division_rules_paragraph"> Ranking will be done with the total of the points on the 10 songs. </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
