    <div class="row">
        <div class="low_division col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 oddIndexPage">
            <div class="odd-title">
                <h2>Low division</h2>
                <p class="odd-paragraph-low-div">Low division features 30 charts splitted by BPM segment from 130 to 210.</p>
                <p class="odd-paragraph-low-div">Each BPM segment has 3 songs, an 11, a 12 and a 13.</p>
                <p class="odd-paragraph-low-div">These are not songs made for the tournament.</p>
                <p class="odd-paragraph-low-div">The scoring system for a song is:
                <strong>Score = 3 * Fantastics + 2 * Excellents + 1 * Greats</strong></p>
                <p class="odd-paragraph-low-div">Only the best score counts on a BPM segment, meaning if you play all the songs from the 130 range, only the best score of the three songs will be counted.</p>
                <p class="odd-paragraph-low-div">Sum of scores from all BPM sections makes a total score which will be used for the ranking.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
