            <div class="even-title">
                <h2>Optional division</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="optional_division_rules_paragraph">This division is not counting towards any specific ranking, it is more or less the Marathon Division.</p>
            <p class="optional_division_rules_paragraph">4 marathons are available for the Low division:
            All 11s, all 12s, all 13s, all songs.</p>
            <p class="optional_division_rules_paragraph">6 marathons are available for the High division:
            First five Beginner charts, first five Expert charts, last five Beginner charts, last five Expert charts (except for the last 2 which are the Hard difficulties), all Beginners, all Experts.</p>
            <p class="optional_division_rules_paragraph">For each marathon, the slowest songs will be played first.</p>
            <p class="optional_division_rules_paragraph">In case it is ever needed, scoring system is the same as the Low division.</p>
